        previous = nil,
        next = nil,
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Rondipur to begin this quest.\n2. Head to Eldieme Necropolis from Batallia Downs (I-10).\n3. As soon as you zone in you will receive a cutscene.\n4. Once the cutscene is over, an NPC named Cannau will spawn.\n   - You will have 30 minutes to complete this quest.\n5. She will begin to run West towards the door at (H-8).  You will either need a [Key Item] Magicked astrolabe, or to bring someone with you, to flip the switch to let you through this door.\n   - Speaking to Cannau will make her stop running.  Talking to her again will make her continue.\n   - Cannau will draw aggro from just about everything inside Eldieme Necropolis. You need to stop her and kill everything in her path.\n   - If her HP drops too low she will blood aggro any undead near by.\n     - She can be cured, so pay attention to her health.\n6. After you get past the gate at (H-8), Cannau will continue to (F-8) taking either the North or South path.\n7. Once she reaches (F-8) she will stop on her own.\n8. Quickly speak to her to obtain the [Key Item] Completion certificate.\n   - If she disappears before you talk to her you will not get credit for escorting her.\n9. Return to Rondipur for your reward.',
        notes = nil,
    },
    ['Exit the Gambler'] = {
