        walkthrough = '1. Start the quest by talking to Aurege (F-3) near Northern San d\'Oria Home Point #4, outside of the Carpenter\'s Guild.\n2. (Optional): Talk to Nonterene (I-10) at the Parade Grounds near Victory Arch.\n3. Varchet is located in Southern San d\'Oria at (L-6) right next to the fountains.\n4. You\'ll need to gamble against him.  Each attempt against him costs 5 gil.  Keep trading until you win.\n   - Gambling against him is still possible after this quest is complete.\n5. After winning, return and talk to Aurege for your reward.',
        notes = '1. This quest does not appear in your log until it is completed.\n2. Exit the Gambler was taken a bit literally when Varchet was temporarily removed from the game in an emergency maintenance in September 2007.\n   - A Moogle was put in his spot, who would inform adventurers that Varchet fell into financial ruin  or had the flu  or something and couldn\'t gamble.\n   - This action was taken due to an exploit where his gambling mini-game could be manipulated by 3rd-party tools, causing an infinite gil glitch.\n   - Varchet returned to his usual spot to try to win his fortune back a few weeks later.',
