        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Ramua in Northern San d\'Oria (E-3) for a cutscene that begins the quest.\n   - You need to have already signed up with the Woodworking Guild for this quest to be activated. Speak to Guild Master: Cheupirudaux - Northern San d\'Oria (F-3)\n2. Ramua will give you the [Key Item] Timber survey checklist and a Hatchet.\n3. Travel to Jugner Forest and log the following items:\n   - Arrowwood Log\n   - Ash Log\n   - Yew Log\n   - Willow Log\n   - Walnut Log\n4. Trade these logs to Ramua, for your reward.  She will also return the logs to you.',
