            {name = '[Key Item] Dragon curse remedy (provided)', count = 1},
        },
        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Arminibit and Ceraulian in Port San d\'Oria (I-9) inside Cargo Room A.\n2. Speak to Novalmauge who walks between (F-8) and (G-8) in Bostaunieux Oubliette Map 1 (enter from Northern San d\'Oria (I/J-6) HP#2 and then Chateau d\'Oraguille (J-8) ) for a cutscene.\n   - Note: If you have not yet completed the quest The Rumor (Drain Quest), you can speak to Novalmauge a second time to accept The Rumor. You no longer need to complete The Rumor before advancing the job quest.\n3. Speak to Morjean in Northern San d\'Oria (L-7), within the Cathedral\'s Manuscript room for a cutscene.\n   - The quest will show up on quests tab now.\n4. Buy a Pickaxe from Ostalie in Southern San d\'Oria (F-8) HP#4\n5. Go to the Maze of Shakhrami and trade a Pickaxe to an Excavation Point to receive a Wyvern Egg. See the map on the right for Excavation Points. (Blue dots)\n6. Return to Morjean and speak to him with the Wyvern Egg in your inventory.\n7. Travel to Meriphataud Mountains (K-8) and look for a ??? near the base of Drogaroga\'s Spine. Trade the Wyvern Egg to it for a cutscene.\n   - Quickest way is the Survival Guide in Castle Oztroja. Step outside and you\'re looking at the spine\'s base.\n8. Speak to Rahal in Chateau d\'Oraguille (H-9).\n   - He will provide you the [Key Item] Dragon curse remedy.\n9. Travel to Ghelsba Outpost to find the Hut Door at (F-10/G-10) to enter a BC fight. Quickest way to BC Entrance is Domenic Teleport NPC in Lower Jeuno.\n   - The enemy in this BC is Wyvern Notorious Monster that is approximately level 40.\n   - Only people up to this point in the quest or players who have already completed the quest may enter this BC.\n   - You are unable to summon trusts in this fight.\n10. Upon defeating the Wyvern, you will receive your reward.\n11. There are more wyvern names to choose from if you pay to rename it.',
        notes = nil,
    },
